{
  "stem": "3382.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First, he said, send out Sula from the ghetto and tell later me where to wait for her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And try to work in the same place in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came Friday night from the work and pulled out some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had sewn in money-- sewn in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started to work in order to organize to take out Sula from the ghetto because only those who had passes could out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It cost some money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I whisked-- she was whisked out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where was your son during this time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she will be taken out with one of commander who gets out and takes out-- I don't know-- empty, empty bags and brings back food or whatever it is, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, she was put-- next day, she was put on the truck and covered with bags and gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the evening, still [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] came up suddenly a man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he says, we are-- we need money because we want to make a present to the German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, at the moment, I don't have money here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would need at least a day or so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would know tomorrow morning, early morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Meantime, I learned probably-- I don't remember-- but probably, I learned from Rachela that she has given my name to that German, who pulled me out because Rachela was taken out by the [NON-ENGLISH], the mafia, the Jewish mafia, you know.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the morning, she ran to the work place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She worked in a-- in a hotel for-- in a former academic house, a dormitory, which was turned into officer hotel, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
